The Facebook post promotes an event offering assistance with the naturalization process.  It does not mention any parliamentary candidates or parties, nor does it advocate for or against any political position. The event's purpose is to provide a service to the community, not to influence electoral outcomes. The post's content and objective do not meet the criteria for electoral propaganda as defined by Article 36 (7) of LEGE nr. 334 din 17 iulie 2006 and Article 98 t) of LEGE nr. 208 din 20 iulie 2015.  The fact that it's a paid advertisement does not automatically qualify it as electoral propaganda; the content itself must be analyzed.
